<section class="failures-section">
  <div class="failures-container">

    <!-- Section title -->
    <h2 class="failures-title">PV Module Failures</h2>

    <!-- Two-column content -->
    <div class="failures-grid">

      <!-- LEFT: Text -->
      <div class="failures-text">
        <p>
          Reliable PV module performance depends on stringent manufacturing
          process controls and well-made components. When manufacturers
          overlook quality assurance and quality control steps or use
          substandard materials, premature failure in modules is likely
          to occur.
        </p>

        <p>
          Today’s projects use technologies and components that did not exist
          25 years ago. Though the long-term reliability of new PV module
          designs cannot be proven with field data, PVEL’s laboratory testing
          simulates and accelerates environmental conditions to replicate
          field failures.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Image -->
      <div class="failures-image">
        <div class="image-card">
            <img
            src="../../../../public/2021/images/INTRO-IEA-PVPS-Failure-Chart_REV.jpg"
            alt="Click here to enlarge the Image"
            loading="lazy"
            />
        </div>

        <p class="image-caption">
            SOURCE: IEA PVPS 2014; LETID AND BACKSHEET FAILURE ADDED BY PVEL, 2019
        </p>
        </div>


    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* Section wrapper */
.failures-section {
  background: #ffffff;
  padding: 96px 0;
  color: #24324a;
}

/* Container */
.failures-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
}

/* Title */
.failures-title {
  font-family: "Asap";
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 72px;
}

/* Grid layout */
.failures-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 460px 520px;
  gap: 80px;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: start;
}

/* Text */
.failures-text p {
  font-family: "Open Sans";
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight:400;
  line-height: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.image-card {
  background: #ffffff;
  padding: 12px;                   
  border-radius: 4px;
  width: 92%;                     
  margin: 0 auto;

  box-shadow:
    0 8px 18px rgba(36, 50, 74, 0.12),
    0 2px 4px rgba(36, 50, 74, 0.08);
}

/* Image itself */
.image-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}

/* Caption */
.image-caption {
  font-family: "Asap";
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-top: 12px;
  color: #24324a;
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .failures-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .failures-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
}
</style>
